{"data":[{"date":"16:00 25/07","title":"V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay Man City, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Juventus-muon-mua-Kante-thay-Pjanic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pjanic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man xanh, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0o tay Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 Italia, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro-172-191834.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic</span> c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Pep \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pjanic v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Man xanh mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Pjanic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mua Kante thay Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay Man City, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante\" title=\"Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Kante, song Juventus v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Kante, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Juventus th\u00ec PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mbappe c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n PSG mua c\u1ef1u sao Leicester. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a Anh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1624","checkdouble":"191995"},{"date":"15:26 25/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-ban-ket-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 25/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 h\u00f4m 21/7 v\u1eeba qua, \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 V.League 2018. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ti\u1ebfn Linh, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea1o c\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng y\u00ean t\u00e2m cho BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean t\u00e2m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-19h00-ngay-257-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V.League ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee3i 'ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p' \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC gi\u01b0\u01a1ng cao, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh l\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00ed do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eb1m d\u1eabn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng V.League, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt g\u00ec \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC b\u1ecb Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i, c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp - m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n>>> Xem th\u00eam: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, Moses, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Samson.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, H.T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Xu\u00e2n Lu\u00e2n, Anh T\u00e0i, L.T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Onyelonu, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Rabo Ali, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1623","checkdouble":"191996"},{"date":"17:04 25/07","title":"HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam 1 ng\u00f4i sao v\u1ec1 Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-emery-tiet-lo-muon-dua-them-1-ngoi-sao-ve-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ante Rebic \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Eintracht Frankfurt. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/MU-muon-mua-Ante-Rebic-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rebic \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ante Rebic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Ante Rebic nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rebic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ante Rebic ghi ban o dau hiep hai mo ti so cho Croatia.\" title=\"Ante Rebic ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Croatia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ante Rebic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Eintracht Frankfurt, song r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Rebic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Sport Bild, M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Rebic, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fred v\u00e0 Dalot.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1622","checkdouble":"191997"},{"date":"15:34 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-dortmund-vs-benfica-7h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dortmund vs Benfica l\u00fac 7h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Dortmund-vs-Benfica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dortmund vs Benfica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Dortmund vs Benfica: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Dortmund \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ICC\u00a02018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 2 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 Man City (1-0) v\u00e0 Liverpool (3-1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i\u00a0ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p Benfica - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia trong bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u00e0 th\u00f4i - Dortmund l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Dortmund kh\u00f4ng an to\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDortmund t\u1eebng th\u1eafng Benfica 4-0 \u1edf Champions League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y Benfica h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u0110N mua b\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Benfica thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15,38 tri\u1ec7u euro\u00a0 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 28,7 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 mua t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Joao Carvalho, Andre Horta hay Raul Jimenez \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Benfica \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla d\u00f9 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u: Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Champions League 2016/17, Benfica th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thua 0-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nDortmund: Marwin Hitz; Toljan, Toprak, Zagadou, Schmelzer; Pulisic, Gotze, Nuri Sahin, Schurrle; Isak.<br>\r\nBenfica: Vlachodimos; Andre Almeida, Conti, Jardel, Grimaldo, Fejsa, Pizzi, Fernandes, Salvio, Rafa Silva, Castillo.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1621","checkdouble":"191998"},{"date":"15:50 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-roma-vs-tottenham-09h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma vs Tottenham l\u00fac 09h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Roma-vs-Tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Roma vs Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Roma vs Tottenham: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, AS Roma v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i\u00a0ICC c\u0169ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\u00a0K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 n\u00e0y, AS\u00a0Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eb1m c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i do Spurs sa s\u00fat m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u do Tottenham thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Pochettino c\u00f3 trong tay \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Lloris, Alli, Kane, Kieran Trippier, Danny Rose, Toby Alderweireld, Jan Vertonghen, Eric Dier v\u00e0 Mousa Dembele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 v\u00e0i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh nh\u01b0 Davinson Sanchez, Christian Eriksen hay Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p AS Roma v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai, HLV Pochettino nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 hay d\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d th\u00ec AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 m\u00e0n th\u1eed l\u1eeda. Do \u0111\u00f3 x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Premier League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 2 tr\u1eadn, AS Roma th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 1.<br>\r\n- T\u1ea1i ICC Cup, AS Roma th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nAS Roma (4-1-2-3): Mirante; Juan, Manolas, Kolarov, Karsdorp; Gonalons; Pastore, Cristante; Schick, Kluivert, Dzeko.<br>\r\nTottenham (4-2-3-1): Vorm; Sanchez, Foyth, Aurier, Davies; Wanyama, Oakley-Boothe; Lamela, Son Heung-min, Lucas; Llorente.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1620","checkdouble":"191999"},{"date":"16:23 25/07","title":"MU d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ante Rebic \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Eintracht Frankfurt. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/MU-muon-mua-Ante-Rebic-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rebic \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ante Rebic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Ante Rebic nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rebic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ante Rebic ghi ban o dau hiep hai mo ti so cho Croatia.\" title=\"Ante Rebic ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Croatia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ante Rebic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Eintracht Frankfurt, song r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Rebic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Sport Bild, M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Rebic, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fred v\u00e0 Dalot.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1619","checkdouble":"192000"},{"date":"16:24 25/07","title":"ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</h2><h2>1. V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u1ec5 th\u1edf</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 25/7, t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) \u0111\u00f3ng \u1edf Kuala Lumpur - Malaysia, \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea7n 1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia ch\u1ec9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eeba c\u00f3 trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd b\u1ed5 sung l\u00e0 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Palestine r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng A, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, c\u00f9ng Hong Kong, \u0110\u00e0i Loan v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. C\u00f2n UAE \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Malaysia.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD 2018 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"ASIAD 2018 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/ASIAD-2018-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-gap-kho-tai-vong-knock-out-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o sau l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 chi\u1ec1u 25/7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf 4 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng D c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho v\u00f2ng knock-out m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt h\u01a1n 1 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i v\u1edf chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u1ea3 quan.&nbsp;Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 UAE t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD 2018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"ASIAD 2018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/ASIAD-2018-Viet-Nam-de-qua-vong-bang,-kho-tho-vong-knock-out-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 mang theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HCV \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham Son Heung-min v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh &lsquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n&rsquo; Jo Hyeon-woo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim Chi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Do \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e9 tr\u00e1nh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\">Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tho\u00e1t c\u1eeda t\u1eed nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00ea &quot;n\u00e9&quot; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim Chi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1ec9 mang t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 viet nam\" title=\"u23 vi\u1ec7t nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-su-menh-giai-cuu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 4/6 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 l\u00e0 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A ho\u1eb7c B.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh 'kh\u1eafc tinh' H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO khi ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua phan chia vong bang mon bong da nam Asiad 2018\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ph\u00e2n chia v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Truc-tiep-boc-tham-bong-da-nam-Asiad-2018-duoc-to-chuc-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ph\u00e2n chia v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Quy t\u1eafc s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn 1: Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A vs Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng C <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 2: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D vs Ba b\u1ea3ng B/E/F <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 3: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B vs Ba b\u1ea3ng A/C/D <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 4: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng F vs Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng E <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 5: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C vs Ba b\u1ea3ng A/B/F <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 6: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E vs Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 7: Nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A vs Ba b\u1ea3ng C/D/E <br>\r\nTr\u1eadn 8: Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B vs Nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng F</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/8/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp t\u1edbi 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\n12 &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-cuoc-chien-khoc-liet-cho-giac-mo-asiad-168-191525.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/dt-olympic-viet-nam-cuoc-chien-khoc-liet-cho-giac-mo-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-cuoc-chien-khoc-liet-cho-giac-mo-asiad-168-191525.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, song h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1618","checkdouble":"192005"},{"date":"17:27 25/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU l\u1ea5y Guardiola ra ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/27/TRUC-TIEP-MU-vs-Man-City-02h00-ngay-2710-Cup-Lien-doan-Anh-2017-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Scholes thay l\u1eddi Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd gh\u00e9t cay gh\u00e9t \u0111\u1eafng phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Old Trafford.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Man Utd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Premier League th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m xa k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.\u201d \u2013 Paul Scholes d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 nu\u1ed1t tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta b\u1ecb Sevilla lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League sau hai m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft FA Cup, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i thua n\u1ed1t Chelsea. C\u1ea3nh tr\u1eafng tay to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn n\u1ed5i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Scholes l\u1ea5y Pep Guardiola ra ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Jose Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Scholes l\u1ea5y Pep Guardiola ra ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Jose Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/27/TRUC-TIEP-MU-vs-Man-City-02h00-ngay-2710-Cup-Lien-doan-Anh-2017-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Scholes l\u1ea5y Pep Guardiola ra ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Jose Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Scholes l\u00e0 v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ch\u00ea bai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua. Khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng, thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a n\u00e0o h\u1ebft nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho th\u1ebf l\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1ed3i, \u00f4ng ta s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i g\u00e2y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Pep Guardiola nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0y h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean l\u00ean m\u1ea5t.\u201d \u2013 Paul Scholes l\u1ea5y Pep Guardiola ra ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Jose Mourinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man City c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u1eeba hoa m\u1ef9 v\u1eeba hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-va-mourinho-can-perisic-hon-bao-gio-het-172-191847.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/goc-nhin-mu-va-mourinho-can-perisic-hon-bao-gio-het.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-va-mourinho-can-perisic-hon-bao-gio-het-172-191847.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n Perisic h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Man United th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Perisic \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh dung ra th\u00f4ng qua ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1617","checkdouble":"192006"},{"date":"17:54 25/07","title":"Bayern Munich b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sao cho Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/bayern-munich-bo-ngo-kha-nang-nhuong-sao-cho-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man Utd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara t\u1eeb Bayern Munich trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago t\u1eeb 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Bayern Munich. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Barcelona, \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2013 khi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Thiago t\u1eeb Bayern Munich \u1edf h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Thiago t\u1eeb Bayern Munich \u1edf h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bayern-munich-bo-ngo-kha-nang-nhuong-sao-cho-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Thiago t\u1eeb Bayern Munich \u1edf h\u00e8 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean cho Thiago khi anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y cho Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u00fap m\u1edf c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 Thiago v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Thiago v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Bayern Munich trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, G\u0110\u0110H Karl-Heinz Rummenigge t\u1ecf ra qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a Thiago, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Bayern v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 s\u1ebd chia tay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Thiago c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i th\u00eau d\u1ec7t n\u00ean.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Man Utd, ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Chelsea c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n cu\u1ed7m Thiago kh\u1ecfi Allianz Arena h\u00f2ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri, t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich-172-191550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-1907-MU-chi-130-trieu-bang-cho-2-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich-172-191550.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m Bayern Munich</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang The Independent \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern-184-191939.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern-184-191939.html\">Chelsea l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Bayern</span><br>\r\nChelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1616","checkdouble":"192007"},{"date":"17:33 25/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Sao Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/7/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Courtois, th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Kh\u00fac m\u1eafc trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ph\u00eda Chelsea.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Keylor Navas th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Los Blancos v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. Sau khi Man United d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 David De Gea, Real \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Real n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chung. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho De Gea l\u00ean m\u1ee9c 350 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 cho Courtois 200 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, k\u00e9m xa nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, khi Real \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, Courtois nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u1edd Daily Express c\u1ee7a Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Courtois.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1edd s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, Real r\u00f3t t\u1edbi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Trong \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Courtois\" title=\"thu mon Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Courtois cho Real. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c m\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t l\u00e0 The Blues ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 Jordan Pickford v\u00e0 Jack Butland r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Gianluigi Donnarumma nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho hay s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3 Courtois. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 26 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid, n\u01a1i 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi con anh \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng. Courtois t\u1eebng c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid t\u1eeb 2011 \u0111\u1ebfn 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-38-tuoi-172-191978.html\">C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/real-muon-mua-pulisic-187-191976.html\">Real nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/anthony-martial-tien-buoc-dai-denchelsea-172-191971.html\">Anthony Martial ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn...Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1615","checkdouble":"192010"},{"date":"09:14 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-ajax-vs-sturm-graz-01h30-ngay-267-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax vs Sturm Graz l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 267 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 267 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Ajax-vs-Sturm-Graz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ajax vs Sturm Graz</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Ajax vs Sturm Graz: 0-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, Sturm Graz t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean thua xa so v\u1edbi Ajax. Ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang con s\u1ed1 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1/Champions League l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u00c1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eady n\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Ajax trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai. Song, xem x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t H\u00e0 lan ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, vi\u1ec7c Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u1ee9 v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e3 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Ajax \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Ajax c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 quan. Tr\u1ea3i qua 7 m\u00e0n th\u1eed l\u1eeda, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2, thua 4, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Walsall, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 Anh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Sturm Graz v\u1eeba m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 t\u1ea1i C\u00fap QG \u00c1o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 6/7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1614","checkdouble":"191970"},{"date":"10:28 25/07","title":"Anthony Martial ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn...Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/anthony-martial-tien-buoc-dai-denchelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho, Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho, Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Khong-hai-long-voi-Mourinho,-Anthony-Martial-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, song HLV\u00a0 Jose Mourinho l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi Old Trafford m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 v\u1edbi San Jose c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i g\u00ec mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, song M.U l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Martial quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial se dut ao chia tay MU he nay\" title=\"Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-247,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Theo The Sun, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n\u00a0s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-martial-co-the-cap-ben-tottenham-vao-tuan-toi-172-187859.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</span>, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. The Blues d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda M.U y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ef1u sao Monaco, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Martial nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford, n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1613","checkdouble":"191971"},{"date":"09:32 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Celtic vs Rosenborg 01h45 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-celtic-vs-rosenborg-01h45-ngay-267-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mat-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-mu-se-da-the-nao-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi-172-191532.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd v\u1eafng t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</span> g\u1eb7p Leicester. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-viec-mat-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 55 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m nay b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/08.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng MU b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi v\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn sang Leicester, n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng sai, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Brighton, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o v\u00ec World Cup. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0 Brighton v\u1edbi M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1612","checkdouble":"191972"},{"date":"10:29 25/07","title":"Everton ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Premier League 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRicharlison t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Everton \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Marco Silva \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Richarlison t\u1eeb CLB Watford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Silva \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 11,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb CLB Brazil Fluminense. Ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 5 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Everton ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169, bom t\u1ea5n Richarlison cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marco Silva. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea1i Watford, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Brazil. Marco Silva c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cEverton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n vinh danh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Marco Silva c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap CLB c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Brazil r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sau l\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span><br>\r\nEverton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\">Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham</span><br>\r\nZaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1611","checkdouble":"191974"},{"date":"10:58 25/07","title":"T\u1edbi Juve, Emre Can tri \u00e2n th\u1ea7y c\u0169","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/16/toi-juve-emre-can-tri-an-thay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang Serie A t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Klopp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Juventus mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. \u0110\u1ec3 n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p, Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Klopp lu\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi t\u00f4i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1eddi Liverpool trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Emre Can c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. Nh\u01b0ng &ldquo;b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i&rdquo;, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp\" title=\"Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c CLB Italia kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Turin, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a CLB.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Champions League. Juve \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fabinho &ndash; Keita.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\">Mourinho: Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n MU \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\">Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1610","checkdouble":"191975"}]}